e qui fait que <strong>douze</strong> nouvelles versions de Gutenberg seront directement int√©gr√©es dans WP 5.3 (les versions&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/04/03/whats-new-in-gutenberg-3rd-april/\">5.4</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/04/17/whats-new-in-gutenberg-17th-april/\">5.5</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/05/01/whats-new-in-gutenberg-1st-may/\">5.6</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/05/15/whats-new-in-gutenberg-15th-may/\">5.7</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/05/29/whats-new-in-gutenberg-29th-may/\">5.8</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/06/12/whats-new-in-gutenberg-12th-june/\">5.9</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/06/26/whats-new-in-gutenberg-26th-june/\">6.0</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/07/10/whats-new-in-gutenberg-10-july/\">6.1</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/07/31/whats-new-in-gutenberg-31-july/\">6.2</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/08/14/whats-new-in-gutenberg-14-august/\">6.3</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/08/28/whats-new-in-gutenberg-28-august/\">6.4</a>, et&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/09/19/whats-new-in-gutenberg-18-september/\">6.5</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Les correctifs de bugs et am√©liorations de performances des versions &nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/10/02/whats-new-in-gutenberg-2-october/\">6.6</a>&nbsp;et&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/10/16/whats-new-in-gutenberg-16-october/\">6.7</a>&nbsp;seront √©galement int√©gr√©s.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Les changements majeurs&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Le temps de chargement pour un article ¬´¬†g√©ant¬†¬ª de 36¬†000 mots et environ 1000 blocs se charge maintenant en 1,5 secondes</li><li>Une nouvelle API pour g√©rer les variations de styles des blocs c√¥t√© serveur (en PHP donc)</li><li>Le